ertainment Boyband Riize</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/j-hope-bts-first-campaign-louis-vuitton-3456272">BTS说唱歌手J-Hope</a>和<a href="https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/louis-vuitton-signs-k-pop-girl-band-le-sserafim-as-brand-ambassadors-1235873569/">Source Music Music Girl Group Le Sserafim</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-lisa-louis-vuitton-newest-brand-ambassador-3777023">Blackpink的邮报丽莎（Lisa）成为路易威登（Louis Vuitton）的最新品牌大使，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
